author: Rory Jones
title: Violence in Israel Continues Despite U.S. Efforts
text:
JERUSALEM—Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu’s assurance to maintain status quo at the flash-point Temple Mount complex in Jerusalem’s Old City, after U.S. Secretary of State John Kerry intervened to calm tensions, failed to halt Palestinian attacks against Israelis on Sunday.
